ClassDecl.Name: GuiComboBoxListControl
ClassDecl.Document: <Document> <summary>Combo box list control. This control is a combo box with a list control in its popup.</summary> </Document>

FuncDecl.Name: GuiComboBoxListControl
FuncDecl.Document: <Document> <summary>Create a control with a specified default theme and a list control that will be put in the popup control to show all items.</summary> <param name="themeName">The theme name for retriving a default control template.</param> <param name="_containedListControl">The list controller.</param> </Document>

FuncDecl.Name: GetItemTemplate
FuncDecl.Document: <Document> <summary>Get the item style provider.</summary> <returns>The item style provider.</returns> </Document>

FuncDecl.Name: SetItemTemplate
FuncDecl.Document: <Document> <summary>Set the item style provider</summary> <param name="value">The new item style provider</param> </Document>

FuncDecl.Name: SetSelectedIndex
FuncDecl.Document: <Document> <summary>Set the selected index.</summary> <param name="value">The selected index.</param> </Document>

FuncDecl.Name: GetItemProvider
FuncDecl.Document: <Document> <summary>Get the item provider in the list control.</summary> <returns>The item provider in the list control.</returns> </Document>
